item.description:
We will be joined by North Bristol County Registrar of Deeds, Barry Amaral. Barry will be discussing facts and figures, foreclosures, NOD's, guiding us through the registry website and answering dozens of questions for our members. As investors, the registry is the heartbeat of our business, information is power.

 

Don't miss the unique opportunity.

 

Hope to see you new investors, old investors, contractors, rehabbers, wholesalers at the meeting in Taunton. Network with the right people!

Net working begins at 6:30, meeting starts at 7pm. See you there.
